Battera::

She flew out of the cave at full tilt.  She stretched her wings and 
felt the wind under her wings.  She closed her eyes as she went 
higher into the air.  She used her sonar to navigate.  It never 
failed her before, why would it now?  She kept her face into the wind 
and enjoyed the freedom of it all.  She used her sonar again, this 
time there was somethig right infront of her.  She opened her eyes 
just intime to see a blurr of color.  She hit something face first at 
full speed.(Starscream)  Stunned, she started to fall to the earth, 
1500 feet below.
